{
  "stem": "3277.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And let them-- and the government knew that this guy has a passport like I had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even I have that paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still have the paper-- Israel was it printed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they let him go to the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went into the train in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they let-- and on the-- on the border, they caught him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That way, I was lucky that I didn't-- if I would fall in the position like this guy, I don't know whether I would be today here and giving your interview.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wish-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother and father would be-- [CRYING] --could see me, you know, at least for an hour.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In those conditions-- in this country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKS] I feel [SOBBING] that my parents had a very bad time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before they got killed, they were thinking, where is Mark, and-- [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I am sure that, when they went to the gas chambers, because they didn't know anything about me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, you're a mother-- you know what it means for a mother about her kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I was maybe 20, 21.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eh-- I-- they were very good parents, even in that-- poor conditions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But very-- a lot of love.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of everything what they could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to do more than they could, in those circumstances, especially Mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
